Load offset 16.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(1). Space: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Returns 0 if absent.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "constraint_upper" takes c as Integer returns Integer:
    If c is equal to 0:
