Note: ============================================================================
Note: CONSTRAINT SATISFACTION
Note: ============================================================================

@Reasoning
Test whether a version satisfies a constraint per the documented ADT
semantics:

  VC_EXACT     : version_compare(v, lower) == 0
  VC_MIN       : version_compare(v, lower) > 0 or
                 (lower_inclusive and == 0)
  VC_MAX       : version_compare(v, upper) < 0 or
                 (upper_inclusive and == 0)
  VC_RANGE     : both VC_MIN and VC_MAX bounds satisfied
  VC_CARET     : v >= lower AND v < upper-cap, where upper-cap depends
                 on the leading non-zero component (Cargo / npm rule)
  VC_TILDE     : v >= lower AND v < lower with minor incremented
  VC_WILDCARD  : v matches lower in all non-wildcarded slots
  VC_ANY       : always true

Prerelease versions are excluded from caret / tilde / wildcard matches
unless the lower bound itself is a prerelease (npm semver "includePrerelease"
default semantics).
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Switch on the kind discriminator and apply the rules using
version_compare. Caret upper bound:
  - major > 0 -> bump major: (major+1, 0, 0)
  - major == 0 and minor > 0 -> (0, minor+1, 0)
  - major == 0 and minor == 0 -> (0, 0, patch+1)
Tilde upper bound:
  - bump minor: (major, minor+1, 0)
Wildcard slots compare the components up to wildcard_at - 1 inclusive.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(p) where p is the prerelease identifier length of inputs. Space:
O(1) plus the temporary Versions allocated for caret / tilde caps.
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Defends against caller-supplied null Versions; returns 0 on any null
input. Pre-release exclusion rule prevents accidentally pulling
"1.0.0-alpha" into a "^1.0.0" range.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "version_satisfies" takes v as Integer, c as Integer returns Integer:
    If v is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    If c is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Let kind be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with c, 0
    If kind is equal to VC_ANY:
        Return 1
    End If
    Let lo be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with c, 8
    Let hi be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with c, 16
    Let lo_inc be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with c, 24
    Let hi_inc be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with c, 32

    If kind is equal to VC_EXACT:
        Let cmp be proc version_compare with v, lo
        If cmp is equal to 0:
            Return 1
        End If
        Return 0
    End If

    If kind is equal to VC_MIN:
        Let cmpm be proc version_compare with v, lo
        If cmpm is greater than 0:
            Return 1
        End If
        If cmpm is equal to 0:
            If lo_inc is equal to 1:
                Return 1
            End If
        End If
        Return 0
    End If

    If kind is equal to VC_MAX:
        Let cmpx be proc version_compare with v, hi
        If cmpx is less than 0:
            Return 1
        End If
        If cmpx is equal to 0:
            If hi_inc is equal to 1:
                Return 1
            End If
        End If
        Return 0
    End If

    If kind is equal to VC_RANGE:
        Let cmplo be proc version_compare with v, lo
        If cmplo is less than 0:
            Return 0
        End If
        If cmplo is equal to 0:
            If lo_inc is equal to 0:
                Return 0
            End If
        End If
        Let cmphi be proc version_compare with v, hi
        If cmphi is greater than 0:
            Return 0
        End If
        If cmphi is equal to 0:
            If hi_inc is equal to 0:
                Return 0
            End If
        End If
        Return 1
    End If

    If kind is equal to VC_CARET:
        Return proc satisfies_caret with v, lo
    End If

    If kind is equal to VC_TILDE:
        Return proc satisfies_tilde with v, lo
    End If

    If kind is equal to VC_WILDCARD:
        Let w_at be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with c, 48
        Return proc satisfies_wildcard with v, lo, w_at
    End If

    Return 0
End Process

@Reasoning
Helper: implement caret rule per Cargo:
  ^X.Y.Z (X > 0)            -> X.Y.Z <= v < (X+1).0.0
  ^0.Y.Z (Y > 0)            -> 0.Y.Z <= v < 0.(Y+1).0
  ^0.0.Z                    -> 0.0.Z <= v < 0.0.(Z+1)
Pre-release versions are excluded unless lower is itself prerelease.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Build the upper-cap Version on the heap, run version_compare, free, return.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(p). Space: O(1) for the transient cap Version.
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Internal helper.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "satisfies_caret" takes v as Integer, lower as Integer returns Integer:
    If lower is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Let cmp_lo be proc version_compare with v, lower
    If cmp_lo is less than 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Let lower_pre be proc version_is_prerelease with lower
    Let v_pre be proc version_is_prerelease with v
    If v_pre is equal to 1:
        If lower_pre is equal to 0:
            Return 0
        End If
    End If
    Let lo_major be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with lower, 0
    Let lo_minor be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with lower, 8
    Let lo_patch be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with lower, 16
    Let cap_major be 0
    Let cap_minor be 0
    Let cap_patch be 0
    If lo_major is greater than 0:
        Set cap_major to lo_major plus 1
        Set cap_minor to 0
        Set cap_patch to 0
    Otherwise:
        If lo_minor is greater than 0:
            Set cap_major to 0
            Set cap_minor to lo_minor plus 1
            Set cap_patch to 0
        Otherwise:
            Set cap_major to 0
            Set cap_minor to 0
            Set cap_patch to lo_patch plus 1
        End If
    End If
    Let cap be proc version_create with cap_major, cap_minor, cap_patch, 0, 0
    If cap is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Let cmp_hi be proc version_compare with v, cap
    proc version_destroy with cap
    If cmp_hi is less than 0:
        Return 1
    End If
    Return 0
End Process

@Reasoning
Helper: implement tilde rule per Cargo:
  ~X.Y.Z -> X.Y.Z <= v < X.(Y+1).0
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Build the upper-cap Version, compare, free.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(p). Space: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Internal helper.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "satisfies_tilde" takes v as Integer, lower as Integer returns Integer:
    If lower is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Let cmp_lo be proc version_compare with v, lower
    If cmp_lo is less than 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Let lower_pre be proc version_is_prerelease with lower
    Let v_pre be proc version_is_prerelease with v
    If v_pre is equal to 1:
        If lower_pre is equal to 0:
            Return 0
        End If
    End If
    Let lo_major be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with lower, 0
    Let lo_minor be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with lower, 8
    Let cap be proc version_create with lo_major, lo_minor plus 1, 0, 0, 0
    If cap is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Let cmp_hi be proc version_compare with v, cap
    proc version_destroy with cap
    If cmp_hi is less than 0:
        Return 1
    End If
    Return 0
End Process

@Reasoning
Helper: implement wildcard rule. Match all components strictly less than
wildcard_at, treat the wildcarded slot and all lower slots as free.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Compare major (always required if wildcard_at >= 1) and minor (required
if wildcard_at >= 2). Pre-release versions are excluded.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(1). Space: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Internal helper.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "satisfies_wildcard" takes v as Integer, lower as Integer, wildcard_at as Integer returns Integer:
    If lower is equal to 0:
        If wildcard_at is equal to 0:
            Return 1
        End If
        Return 0
    End If
    Let v_pre be proc version_is_prerelease with v
    If v_pre is equal to 1:
        Return 0
    End If
    If wildcard_at is equal to 0:
        Return 1
    End If
    Let lo_major be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with lower, 0
    Let v_major be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with v, 0
    If lo_major is not equal to v_major:
        Return 0
    End If
    If wildcard_at is equal to 1:
        Return 1
    End If
    Let lo_minor be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with lower, 8
    Let v_minor be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with v, 8
    If lo_minor is not equal to v_minor:
        Return 0
    End If
    Return 1
End Process
